title: Microsoft Office 2016 16.0.4266.1001 VL Select Edition by SPecia

Official website: the Microsoft
Language: English and Russian

Additional Information:

Besides the new design, made in the style of Windows 10, the package received some important innovations in terms of functionality.
In particular, it was deepened integration with cloud services that allegedly helped simplify work with documents on a variety of devices, including simultaneous editing of the same file multiple users.
In addition, when sending bulk emails attachments in Outlook can now automatically upload them to the repository OneDrive. As an auxiliary tool in Office 2016 came the so-called "smart" applications (Smart Applications),
such as search commands to perform certain actions Tell Me and sorter incoming messages Clutter, based on machine learning technologies.
